# 依赖与构建产物
node_modules/

# 评测运行目录（runs/round<N>/<run>/）：默认不进 git，只放行各 run 顶层的对话记录导出（transcript.md/html）
image-flow/runs/**
!image-flow/runs/*/
!image-flow/runs/*/*/
!image-flow/runs/*/*/transcript.md
!image-flow/runs/*/*/transcript.html

# gstack 变体是 46MB 第三方仓库快照（布局有缺陷待重做），只保留顶层 SKILL.md 供查证
skill-variants/gstack/home/skills/gstack/*
!skill-variants/gstack/home/skills/gstack/SKILL.md
